Package ca.cgjennings.apps.arkham.plugins

Class InstalledLibrary

java.lang.Object
ca.cgjennings.apps.arkham.plugins.InstalledBundleObject
ca.cgjennings.apps.arkham.plugins.InstalledLibrary
All Implemented Interfaces:
IconProvider, Comparable<InstalledBundleObject>
public final class InstalledLibrary extends InstalledBundleObject
Represents an installed library. Generally, much less information is available about libraries than about other kinds of bundle objects because library bundles do not contain specific plug-ins.
Since:
3.0
See Also:
BundleInstaller.getInstalledLibraries()
